      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for internal research use with trained analysts.",
      "rationale": "Model is operated exclusively by trained CFD engineers within the research group. Formal use-error assessment not required at MRL 2. Standard operating procedures for simulation setup are maintained in the group's quality management documentation."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model form",
