      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; model form selection documented in technical basis.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model and power-law hemolysis model selected based on published literature for blood pump applications. Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2. Selection rationale recorded in simulation plan."
