    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 1 requirements at MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application. This model has been applied in clinical research to support Class II device submissions and the assessment team finds the evidence package sufficient under the Minimal profile declaration.",
